\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces WebRTC call establishment sequence. Steps~1--3 use supporting infrastructure (STUN server, signaling server). Once ICE selects a path and DTLS establishes encryption (steps~4--5), media flows directly between the two browsers (step~6). The signaling server plays no further role in the media path.}}{12}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:webrtc-sequence}{{3}{12}{WebRTC call establishment sequence. Steps~1--3 use supporting infrastructure (STUN server, signaling server). Once ICE selects a path and DTLS establishes encryption (steps~4--5), media flows directly between the two browsers (step~6). The signaling server plays no further role in the media path}{figure.3}{}}
